                <p>
                    <lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied></hi> koccaṭapaṉmar tiripuvaṉaccakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>cuntarapāṇṭiyatevarkku yāṇ <gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> 
                    <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> tar <hi rend="grantha">śiṣya</hi>ril cāriputtirapaṇṭitaṉeṉ naṭuvil nāṭāṉa Irā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>vaḷanāṭṭu vecālip <gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> 
                    <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> Eṉṉutāy nāṉ Aṉupavittu varukiṟa Iraṇṭān tākkil melpāṟkellai <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
                    <lb n="4"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> lattukkut teṟkum Innāṉkellaiyuḷ naṭuvupaṭṭa mikutikkuṟaivu Uṭpaṭṭa <g type="nilam"/> 1 <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
                    <lb n="5"/>ceytu potukaṟ pūcaikkum Iṟṟai nāḷil Eḻuntaruḷiyirunta caṅkattārkkut tāṉa <gap reason="lost" quantity="11" unit="character"/> 
                    <lb n="6"/>paṭṭa pākāciriya Urimaikaḷum Akappaṭa Ikkoyilukku nāṉ Uvāppaṭikkuc <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
                </p>
                
